title: Sake House
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese restaurant. Menu has a vegetarian hand roll portion which include a cucumber roll, avocado roll, asparagus roll, and sweet potato roll -- all of which are reported to be vegan (but do ask about mayonaise). There's also edamame, numerous salads, yaki noodles with vegetables, and a vegetable side dish.
